            "title": "中港股市午後齊回吐 港股失兩萬七 滬深A股曾倒跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深北證交所中午公布上調融資保證金比例，午後即時推低中港兩市股市。港股回落至兩萬七以下，滬深兩市股市更曾倒跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：上海證券交易所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20230828_FI_source-web_SSE.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：上海證券交易所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20230828_FI_source-web_SSE.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：上海證券交易所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數下午甫開市即失守27000點，截至下午約1時23分升幅收窄至57點，報26905點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)跌幅擴大至約3.7%；中國平安(02318)跌約2.6%，中國人壽(02628)也跌約1.9%。相反，阿里巴巴(09988)依然強勢，升幅暫僅收窄至約4.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15581447-%e4%b8%ad%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e9%bd%8a%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%a4%b1%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e5%80%92%e8%b7%8c",
